{"article_id":"KUJO6Wrhht65GLwn","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Donald Trump says","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"he will close down the US government","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"if necessary","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"to build his wall along the Mexico border .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"The president told supporters at a `` Make America Great Again '' rally in Phoenix , Arizona ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"that the opposition Democrats were being `` obstructionist '' .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"During the 80-minute speech , he also took aim at the media ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"blaming them for giving far right groups `` a platform '' .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"But he selectively quoted his initial response to violence at a far-right rally","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"that left one woman dead .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"He omitted the much-criticised claim","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"that `` many sides '' had to shoulder the blame for violence in Charlottesville , Virginia .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"President Trump wants Congress to finance his controversial plan","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"to build a `` big , beautiful '' wall along the United States ' border with Mexico","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"to keep out illegal immigrants .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"But Republicans will need the support of Democrats","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"to secure funding for the wall in a government spending bill ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"which they are unlikely to get .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"In his speech , Mr Trump said","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"the Democrats were `` putting all of America 's safety at risk ''","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"by opposing the wall .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"immigration officers","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"who worked in the area","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"said","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"it was `` vital '' to stem the flow of illegal immigrants .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"that ,","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"if it came to it ,","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"he would risk a government shutdown","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"- which is what happens","depth":15},{"id":31,"text":"when legislation","depth":17},{"id":32,"text":"funding the federal government","depth":17},{"id":33,"text":"can not be passed by Congress","depth":16},{"id":34,"text":"and non-essential services stop .","depth":14},{"id":35,"text":"`` Now the obstructionist Democrats would like us not to do it ,","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"but believe me","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"if we have to close down our government ,","depth":14},{"id":38,"text":"we are building that wall , ''","depth":14},{"id":39,"text":"Mr Trump said ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"that `` the American people voted for immigration control '' .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"If President Trump wants a government shutdown","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"all","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"he has to do","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"is refuse to sign a funding bill","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"sent to him by Congress .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"Capitol Hill is set to debate a new budget measure this autumn ,","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"and","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"unless it is passed","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"federal operations will be in limbo by 1 October .","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"Donald Trump 's signature campaign promise","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"- to `` build that wall '' -","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"epitomised his appeal to the nation , an apparently simple solution to a problem","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"freighted with racial and economic undertones .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Not only that but it would be free !","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"Mexico would pay ,","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"as Mr Trump and his cheering crowds repeatedly insisted .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"But it turns out that governing is harder than campaigning .","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"Construction of prototypes near San Diego in California","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"- which had been scheduled for this summer -","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"has been delayed until at least December by a legal challenge from one rejected bidder .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Ranchers , environmentalists and some businesses on the border have raised objections to the plan ,","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"while one Republican congressman in Texas , Will Hurd , has even described the wall as the most expensive and least effective way","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"to secure the border .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Mexico ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"needless to say ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"is not keen to write a cheque .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Faced with the need","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"to win over doubters on the detail ,","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"and explain why this would be a lot of money well spent ,","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"Mr Trump has instead chosen to raise the stakes with an `` all or nothing '' approach .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"President Trump attacked the media in the campaign-style speech ,","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"reporters had misrepresented his `` perfect '' words in the wake of the violence in Charlottesville ,","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"where Heather Heyer was killed","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"after a car ploughed into a crowd of people","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"protesting against far-right demonstrators","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"including neo-Nazis .","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"He accused `` truly dishonest people in the media and the fake media '' of `` trying to take away our history and heritage ''","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"because ,","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"he said ,","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"they `` do n't like our country '' .","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"He quoted his first public response to the violence on 12 August ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"which was criticised by both Republicans and Democrats","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"for not explicitly condemning the far-right .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"`` This is what I said on Saturday :","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"'We 're closely following the terrible events","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"unfolding in Charlottesville , Virginia , ' -","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"this is me speaking .","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"'We condemn in the strongest possible terms this egregious display of hatred , bigotry and violence . ' That 's me speaking on Saturday , right after the event , ''","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"But his full quote was :","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"`` We condemn in the strongest possible terms this egregious display of hatred , bigotry and violence on many sides , on many sides . ''","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"Separately , the UN Committee on the Elimination of Racial Discrimination has criticised the US for what it said","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"was a `` failure at the highest political level ''","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"to reject `` racist violent events '' .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"Referring to Charlottesville ,","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"the committee said","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"it was issuing a rare `` early warning '' ,","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"which has been used in recent years in countries","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"including Burundi , Iraq , Nigeria and the Ivory Coast .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"Nafta :","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"The US , Mexico and Canada have begun talks","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"on revising their trade deal ,","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"and negotiators are due to meet again on 1 September .","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"But Mr Trump said","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"he thought","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"he would `` probably end up terminating Nafta ''","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"The US , Mexico and Canada have begun talks","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"on revising their trade deal ,","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"and negotiators are due to meet again on 1 September .","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"But Mr Trump said","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"he thought","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"he would `` probably end up terminating Nafta ''","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"North Korea :","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"He sounded hopeful about a reduction in tensions .","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"Referring to North Korean leader Kim Jong-un ,","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"Mr Trump said :","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"`` I respect the fact","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"that he is starting to respect us . ''","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"He added :","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"`` And maybe - probably not ,","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"but maybe - something positive can come about ''","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"He sounded hopeful about a reduction in tensions .","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"Referring to North Korean leader Kim Jong-un ,","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"Mr Trump said :","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"`` I respect the fact","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"that he is starting to respect us . ''","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"He added :","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"`` And maybe","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"- probably not ,","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"but maybe -","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"something positive can come about ''","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"Sheriff Joe Arpaio :","depth":7},{"id":135,"text":"The US president hinted","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"he would pardon the controversial former Arizona sheriff ,","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"who rose to national prominence","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"because of his tough stance against illegal immigration .","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"that Joe Arpaio","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"- who was found guilty of criminal contempt in July over his detention of migrants -","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"`` is going to be just fine '' ,","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"but he would not yet formally pardon him","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"because `` I do n't want to cause any controversy ''","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"Responding to the speech ,","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"the former National Intelligence director James Clapper told CNN","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"that he was questioning Donald Trump 's `` fitness '' for office .","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"`` I also am beginning to wonder about his motivation for it , ''","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"he said ,","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"he found the rally `` downright scary and disturbing '' .","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"Ruben Gallego , a Democratic Party congressman in Arizona , said","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"it was the worst-ever speech by a US president .","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"`` It was all about him ,","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"it was not about the country , ''","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"he told the BBC .","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"A former British ambassador to the US , Peter Westmacott , said","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"he saw parallels with the establishment of Nazi Germany in 1933 .","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"`` President Trump did an amazing job tonight .","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"His message is uniting our great nation ! `` ,","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"tweeted Ryan Fournier , the head of Students for Trump .","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"White Nationalist Richard Spencer tweeted :","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"`` Trump has never denounced the Alt-Right .","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"Nor will he . ''","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"While Mr Trump 's comments were met with cheers inside the conference centre ,","depth":9},{"id":166,"text":"anti-Trump protesters","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"who had gathered outside the rally","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"clashed with police","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"after the rally had finished .","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"A police spokesman in the city said","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"at least four arrests were made","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"after protesters threw bottles and rocks .","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"Get news from the BBC in your inbox , each weekday morning","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":347,"left":346,"right":173,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":346,"left":224,"right":345,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":224,"left":185,"right":223,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":179,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":177,"right":178,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":0,"right":176,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":176,"left":1,"right":175,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":184,"left":180,"right":183,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":180,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":181,"right":182,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":181,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":223,"left":219,"right":222,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":219,"left":190,"right":218,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":190,"left":187,"right":189,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":12,"right":186,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":186,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":189,"left":15,"right":188,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{